title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 6 2022
description:
Former prosecutor Andy McCarthy of National Review and Fox News joins Clay and Buck to discuss the appointment of a special master to go through the documents seized at Mar-a-Lago. C&B welcome a new affiliate, KFOY in Reno, Nevada. How many Eliza Fletchers have Democrat crime polices killed? White House Press Secretary Karine Jean-Pierre refers to the "Nordstrom" pipeline instead of Nord Stream 2. C&B take a call on crime.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
